      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">The Connected Member: AI is Rewriting Membership Sales and Nobody's Ready</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">It's 9 PM on a Tuesday. Someone asks their AI coach to find them a gym. If your business doesn't have structured, machine-readable intelligence, you're invisible.</p>
